# Stack Baseline

Use pnpm, TypeScript strict, TanStack Start/Router, React, shadcn/ui + Tailwind,
PostgreSQL + Drizzle, Dexie IndexedDB caches/drafts/future saves, Vitest, Playwright,
Biome, Docker, and Dokploy. No npm/yarn, ESLint, Prettier, Redux, Zustand, real
club/player names, or localStorage game state/cache/drafts.

SurrealDB is deferred and not the system of record. Do not apply SurrealDB
patterns unless Nico re-ratifies that direction in the vault.
